<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued February 27 at 3:51PM EST until February 27 at 8:00PM EST by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM EST THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...Mixed precipitation. Additional snow accumulations of
less than a half inch and ice accumulations of a light glaze.
Winds gusting as high as 35 mph.
* WHERE...Lapeer and St. Clair Counties.
* WHEN...Until 8 PM EST this evening.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the evening commute.
* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Snow covered roads with additional light
icing and/or snow accumulations possible through 8 PM will
create hazardous conditions for the evening commute.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
